Why Container?
- Various SWs - Versioning Issues
- Virtualization vs Containerization
- DevOps - Agile, Quick creation of Infra
- Scalability/Reliability
- Security Issues - SecOps
- Microservices - Hosting Env.
- Cattles vs Pets
- Application Virtualization

LXC, LXD
Docker Ecosystem
- Docker Images
- Docker Container
- Docker Runtime
- Docker Networking
- Docker Storage Volumes
- Docker Swarm

Complex Multitier Impln

-i - Interactive mode
-t - Block Exiting
-d - daemon

-td - Block Exiting and daemon
-it - Interactive and Block exiting

Container Life Cycle Methods
----------------------------
docker run -td ubuntu
sudo docker stop 67ab3a7
sudo docker start 67ab3a7
sudo docker pause 67ab3a7
sudo docker unpause 67ab3a7
sudo docker kill 67ab3a7

sudo docker inspect 67ab3a7

Creating Docker Image
---------------------
1) Create folder - mywebapp
1.1) mywebapp/images, /pages
2) Create dockerfile - specify instructions
3) docker build - tagging(identifier)
4) docker run - local repository

4) docker push - push it on docker hub/remote repo
5) docker pull
6) docker run

sudo docker build -t omspandey/mydockerimage:1.0 .


